Most E-Commerce brands struggle to scale their ads PROFITABLY for 3 main reasons:
‚ùå #1 They spend the same amount of money every day (and every hour of the day) instead of distributing their advertising dollars to the specific days of the week (and hours of the day) when they historically make the most sales.
